modules.description: This module implements low-level I2C communication primitives for interacting with I2C devices. It provides functions to set device addresses and perform standard I2C operations including quick writes, byte and word data transfers, block reads and writes, and process calls. These operations work directly with I2C device file descriptors and raw numeric types such as Stdint.uint8 and Stdint.uint16, reflecting the wire-level data representation.
